# Module: tf.keras.applications



Defined in [`tensorflow/keras/applications/__init__.py`](https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.10/tensorflow/keras/applications/__init__.py).

Keras Applications are canned architectures with pre-trained weights.
